Use this folder for heavier app-level models that are shared across features but are not just reusable UI-facing helper types.

Put a type here when:
- it represents app-wide state or domain concepts
- multiple features rely on it
- it should not live under `Common/Models` because it is more central than presentational

Examples for `Steps_UI` could include shared activity summaries, goal types, or persisted app configuration models used by multiple screens.
